## Workflow
1. Read this file
2. Read root /readme.md
3. Read /markdown/readme.md
4. Read `/markdown/policy/` if unsure about naming, organization, or other policies
5. Make changes
6. Date-stamp any new .md or /ai-tools/ files
7. NOTIFY: "Done with [change]"